Name
       redraw - Refreshes the display in the viewable window

Syntax
       redraw [-help]

       Refreshes the display in the viewable window. This command performs the
       same  function  as  the Redraw icon (CTRL+R keyboard shortcut). You can
       use this command at any stage in the design flow.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description of the redraw command.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man  command:
              man redraw.

